
Description
    Output a bang as a metronome

Category
    Time

Arguments
    Float: period (1000)
    Float: quantum (1)
    Symbol: unit ('millisecond')

Options

Inlet 1
    Bang: start metro
    Stop: stop metro
    Float: 1/0 start and stop
    Unit: set time base

Inlet 2
    Float: set period

Outlet 1
    Bang: bang at a periodic time
